## 4_loop_while.med
## Continuous (while loop) — count even/odd numbers from -5 to 5

Admission <: :> [:
    Organ number =: DoseMinus 5 |

    Continuous <: number MinSafe 5 :> [:
        Observe <: "%d", number :> |

        Diagnose <: number DoseMod 2 Match 0 :> [:
            Observe <: " : is EVEN\n" :> |
        :] Alternate [:
            Observe <: " : is ODD\n" :> |
        :]

        number =: number DosePlus 1 |
    :]
:]
